Sorry I wasn't on all day, there was a rather unexpected family trip 
that I had to attend.

::Prowl::

Prowl could feel the pain in hear head along with the confusion as 
she recieved his words.

"My thoughts, love. Can you feel my feelings and memories like I can 
feel yours?"

He was a bit confused by all this, but he could see the many ways 
that this new ability could bring them closer together, and he liked 
the possibilities.






--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, "Megan Solmonson" <tmrattrap@h...> wrote:
>

all...it was

> Iron Raptor just sighs, leaning back and then looking down at her 
hands.
> Strange, she could almost pass for an organic...only her insides 
here all 
> machine.
> But then she suddenly heard a voice in her mind, much like Prowls.
> Snapping her head to look up to him after the voice died away, 
though she 
> had understood what he had said.
> Though, it hurt her head a bit too.*
> 
> " What was that?"
> 
> * She spoke out loud.*
